name: Purple and yellow 12month Tutu
description: This Purple and Yellow tutu is made to fit the average 1 year old. Perfect for spring, summer, birthdays, photos and just for general dress up!

name: Newborn Black and Pink Tutu
description: This is a handmade black and hot pink tutu. It is about 12in round and will stretch up to about 19in+. It can either be flared out as it is in the picture or down so it'll hang from babies waist.

name: Custom Tutu Dress
description:
Your choice of colour(s), length, and size. Also your choice of if you'd like for it to poof out or hang down on the legs. 

Once you place the order email me at: Emily_joy@live.com with details, I will need the baby/toddlers waist measurement as well as how long you'd like for it to be, also if you want it to poof out or hang down on the legs. I will also need to know what colour(s) you'd like.

Typically I can do whatever colour(s) you'd like, but if by chance I can't you will receive an email back as soon as possible.

Turn around is about 1-2 weeks, if you need it sooner be sure to let me know.
